column1:
You're so effin' strong! You shoulda told us
right away you could fight!

Not just that, but your clothes! What in the
world...?

It's completely different from our own
transformations.
I copied what you do and ended up like this.
Right? It's not just the clothes...
Dude, that ain't the issue... More importantly?
Yeah, this ain't just about the clothes.
Uh, are you some kinda Persona-user?

The things you were using during the fight—
those boxes flying around.
That was a weapon. I needed it to fight.
Sophia... Just what in the world ARE you?
Yeah, we already heard that one.

Hmm... There's still just too much we don't
know.

But we don't have the time to figure it out now,
either. Getting out of here needs to be our
number one priority.

Yeah, we really don't need her getting any more
attention from the enemy.

Hey, let's just have her help us out! Considering
what we just saw, I don't think we'll have a
problem.

Agreed. We have no idea what's ahead of us;
the more firepower, the better.
Can you lend us a hand, Sophia?
Right. You'll be counting on me.
Right. I won't push myself too hard.
Well, let's move! Lead the way, Shorty!
